\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 As with any roleplay game, the centre of the game is your characters, creating your characters will be done using the Fate deck, following the rules set out, though there are optional parts in it}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Characteristics}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 In LoH there are eight characteristics, Strength, agility, will, intelligence, co-ordination, charsima consciousness constitution, each skill is linked to a characteristic.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 At character creation the maximum that a characteristic can total is 10, and the maximum it can be increased to is 15.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Strength: What it says on the tin, gives you your bonus damage dice in close combat, along with your constitution make up your starting hit points.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Agility: The skill that is linked to Close Combat}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Will: Linked to magical resistance, divine magic, and arcane magic used by shamans and morale}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Intelligence: Linked to the use of arcane magic by wizards and War Mages, the resistance of Psionics}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Co-ordination: Linked to the use of ballistic weapons}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Charisma: Linked to the use of psionics, arcane magic by sorcerers and magic using minstrels }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Consciousness: Linked to several skills including }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Constitution: Linked to Resistance to physical damage}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
