\par\pard\plain \fi720\sl480\slmult1\ql\ltrch\loch {\*\bkmkstart The_Fate_Deck}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The Fate deck is used for a number of different things in a game of Legends of Hamanshiron.}{\*\bkmkend The_Fate_Deck}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Each character begins with at least 2 fate points to cheat fate in a game, to land a blow when it might otherwise have missed, to pull off a spell that saved the life of a comrade who would otherwise have perished, to change an otherwise deadly cut to a nasty little nick, all these and more }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The deck can be replaced by a standard deck of cards.}
