\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Skill checks are taken on d20's at easy on a single d20 requring a score of at or under the skill score (10+ability score+skill points) Intermediate checks on 2d20 at or under skill score (5+ability score+skill points) hard checks on 3d20 at or under skill score (ability score+ skill points) extremely difficult 4d20 skill score (ability score +skill points - 5) and near impossible (ability score + skill points - 10) note rolls of 1 are always passes and cause a critical pass and rolls of 20 always fails causing critical failure.}
