\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The breakdown of a turn:}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Players draw a card from the Fate deck to determine the order of initiative, the GM then draws a card for each mob, leader and NPC in the fight. The GM puts them in a row order  of first to last. Each actor's token goes in front of their cards }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The first of four sequences begins with the actor with the highest initiative beginning their first stage, taking three standard actions and one free action, once they have completed their stage, the actor with the next highest initiative takes their stage until all of the actors have completed their stage, the first sequence is completed.}
